Project Description
The uWebshop contribution project is an addition to the closed source uWebshop solution for Umbraco.
This contribution project is made available to create and exchange payment providers, user controls and anything else build using the uWebshop API.


More information can be found via our website:
http://www.uWebshop.com 

and our Twitter account:
http://twitter.com/uWebshop
